  "text": "Media. Saline waste water (SWW) was produced by electrodialysis of cheese whey (EWDU 6xEDR-II/250-0.8; MEGA a.s., Czech Republic) in a dairy company (Moravia Lacto a.s., Czech Republic). The SWW was pre-treated as described in [CITATION_1] .",
